node.text: This is from last year when we were blessed with the opportunity to rebuild Jose Caballero’s truck after he and his family were harassed by a group of idiots during a camping trip. This moment was when we revealed to him the brand new camp trailer and Polaris General that we were able to give him along with his truck upgrades. This is still one of the coolest things I’ve ever been blessed to be part of 💯

node.text:
I never thought I’d be the ‘post a firework video on social media’ kind of guy but watching last nights firework show from the @pavatiwake AL26 on Flathead Lake last night was something straight out of a storybook and I couldn’t help but share. Thank you @callmemayor for the incredible show and thank you @pavatiwake @jeff.mahaffey for building this insane boat 💥🇺🇸💥

HAPPY INDEPENDENCE DAY!
